                <h1>Trends 2018: The ransomware revolution</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Tracing the evolution and subsequent revolution of ransomware</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
                <div class="wls-author with-avatar">
                            <div class="wls-author-avatar">
